#

Tuna Stuffed Avocado

10 min
$7.5
360 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

fishdairy

Dietary Tags:

low-carbgluten-freehigh-protein

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

quick mealhealthyno-cook

Description

A refreshing and healthy dish featuring creamy avocado filled with a savory tuna mix.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • canned tuna (drained): 1 can (5 oz)
  • greek yogurt: 1/4 cup
  • celery (finely chopped): 1/4 cup
  • red onion (finely chopped): 2 tablespoons
  • lime juice: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • paprika: a pinch
